defaultRaising the small claims track limitdefault - 
defaultThe car insurers are actively lobbying for the small claims track limit to be raised to £5,000 from the current level of £1,000.  
defaultOur arguments against the raising of the small claims limit can be summarised as:
default&#xa0;
defaultAt the very least
